title: World Doctor Alliance
cleaned_text: The World Doctor Alliance does not have a consensus of opinions on the origin of COVID-19 or the political ramifications of the lockdown in general. Instead, it represents a wide range of viewpoints held by healthcare experts. WDA is nevertheless determined to discuss the reasons of harm brought on by the coronavirus act measures and to bring up concerns that reveal dangerous medical and life-limiting procedures detrimental to the health of all living people—men, women, and children.
